Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}もしも薔薇に棘がなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}手折りやすくなるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}薔薇は薔薇でなくなり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}そう偽りの花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:40.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}棘を備えたまま咲いてるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.79,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}薔薇の運命か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:46.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}人も何か決められて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:49.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}生まれ落ちる運命か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:53.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}教えて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:57.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}あらかじめ決められた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}私の進む道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}もしも運命の女神が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}味方するなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:11.14,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}その道は虹色の花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.00,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}咲き乱れるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:19.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}願う想いどうか叶えて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.21,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果玫瑰沒有了刺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.70,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}變得伸手易折
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.08,0:22:32.94,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}玫瑰也將失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.71,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}變成虛假之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:40.00,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}永遠只能帶刺盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.79,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}是玫瑰的宿命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:46.18,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}有些事情早已注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.49,0:22:49.44,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}也是人的宿命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:53.14,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:57.73,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我的前進之路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.58,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}早已命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.67,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}如果命運女神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.24,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}願與我並肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:11.14,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}那就讓七彩之花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.00,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}一路盛放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:19.85,ED-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}這是我唯一的願望
